paragraphs.title: PERSONS WITH >50% PROBABILITY OF HEART DISEASE
paragraphs.text:
%sql

SELECT PERSON_ID, PREDICTION PRED,ROUND(PROBABILITY,3) PROB, ROUND(COST,2) COST 
  FROM APPLY_RESULT WHERE PREDICTION = 1 AND PROBABILITY > 0.5 
  ORDER BY PROBABILITY DESC;

paragraphs.title: PREDICTION ON A NEW RECORD
paragraphs.text:
%sql
SELECT ROUND(PREDICTION_PROBABILITY(neural_network, '1' USING 
                                    55 AS AGE, 
                                     1 AS SEX, 
                                     2 AS CP,
                                     133 AS TRESTBPS,
                                     250 AS CHOL,
                                     0 AS FBS,
                                     1 AS RESTECG,
                                     125 AS THALACH,
                                     0 AS EXANG,
                                     0.7 AS OLDPEAK,
                                     1 AS SLOPE,
                                     1 AS CA,
                                     2 AS THAL),3) PROBABILITY_HEART_DISEASE
  FROM DUAL;
